*******VIM*******
save: :w
save and exit: :wq
exit: :q
force: ! (example :w! :q!)
vertical split: open a document and then type :vsplit /path-to-document/document and this will open the specified document and split the screen so you can see both documents.
copy: y
copy a line: yy
paste: p
cut: d
cut a line: dd

*****NGINX******
sudo apt update //to update all the ubuntu modules
sudo apt install nginx
nginx -v  //version
sudo service start nginx or sudo service stop nginx or sudo service nginx restart  (Ab hamara by defualt nginx server start ho jata ha and by chance agr na ho to server ko hum srat stop kr skte ha khud) (https://linuxhandbook.com/system-has-not-been-booted-with-systemd/)
service nginx status
for replacing apche2 with nginx(http://tyhoffman.com/blog/2012/04/remove-apache2-install-nginx/)**
